name: Zero Progress Demo Audio Cassette Tape
description: Zero Progress has been causing a stir with their vicious live shows in the Bay Area since their formation in the mid-summer, uncomprimising hardcore featuring members of bands you either don't know or don't care about. But, that is beside the point. What matters is, this 9 song tape is a ripper, coming from four dudes who have spent a few too many hours listening to DYS and Negazione records. Limited to 50 copies, get 'em while they're hot
